Upon release from imprisonmt, dft shall be on supervised release for 2 yrs and folloiwng spec cond 1) dft is prohibited from possessing firearms or other dangerous weapons. 2) if deported, dft not to return to US without permission from the Atty General or Immigration Service. 3) If dft re-enters the US during supervised release period, he is required to ntfy US Prob Officer for the Dist of Oregon and the US atty for the Dist of Oregon. sgd Bu 4/12/90 m 4/17/90 (1)
